latestPosts.caption: Being a saree girl, the feeling of wearing traditional heritage weaves from beautiful artisans in our country is unmatched. Went across to @kankatala_ and picked this gold beauty — it instantly caught my eye with its rich texture and timeless elegance. I chose it for a cocktail evening, and it turned out to be the perfect blend of tradition and contemporary glam. The versatility of this weave lets me style it up for a chic night out or down for a more classic occasion. There’s truly something magical about draping heritage in a modern setting.

Here’s a sneak peak into my sitting space and the canvas that was the starting point for my entire vision. The colour, the texture and the turn around time by @creton.inc was brilliant. Exactly what was shown as a sample, done beautifully by the entire team. A little bit of my cozy space 🤎

Each time I travel, an element of fashion comes with me wherever I go. And how one may wonder? With tbe #ManishMalhotraXSamsonite bag. It’s unmissable and makes you want to pose! Go try yours now #ManishMalhotraXSamsoniteVibeCheck🤍
